+**Control/monitoring objects:**
+*   ***Routing & load balancing*** — token balance by experts, preventing hot experts and stragglers (p95/p99).
+*   ***Communication-aware scheduling*** — all-to-all network/topology accounting, inter-node traffic minimization.
+*   ***Placement & EP degree*** — placement of device/node experts and choice of degree of expert parallelism.
+
+The parallelisms and operator structure are the fundamental concepts that are used in LLM inference planning, scheduling and error handling.
